-- clikae launcher template. Two placeholders are substituted by
-- lib/commands/app.sh at generation time (the SHELL_CMD token below becomes the
-- env-prefixed CLI command; the TITLE token becomes the Terminal window title,
-- e.g. claude (work)). They appear only on the two code lines, so substitution
-- never touches this comment.

on run
    tell application "Terminal"
        activate
        set newTab to do script "@SHELL_CMD@"
        set custom title of newTab to "@TITLE@"
    end tell
end run
